# Benchmark Results Directory

Timestamped benchmark results are stored here.

Structure:
```
results/
├── windows_20260201_120000/
│   ├── platform_time.log
│   ├── ecs_world.log
│   ├── SUMMARY.md
│   ├── industry_comparison.md
│   └── comparison.md (if compared with baseline)
└── linux_20260201_130000/
```

Results are automatically generated by:
```bash
./scripts/benchmark_all_platforms.sh
```
